    public class ServiceElementWidget
extends com.emitrom.lienzo.client.core.shape.Group
implements com.emitrom.lienzo.client.core.event.NodeMouseClickHandler, com.emitrom.lienzo.client.core.event.NodeDragStartHandler, com.emitrom.lienzo.client.core.event.NodeDragMoveHandler, com.emitrom.lienzo.client.core.event.NodeDragEndHandler
    The ServiceElementWidget class represents a Service Element Widget object displaying on the screen. This is a subclass class extended from com.emitrom.lienzo.client.core.shape.Group. It includes element icon image, multiple lines and text label so that they can be moved around together by mouse
